Key Match Events: Alec Bohm went 4-for-5 with one home run and four RBIs, including a three-run homer in the fourth inning that turned a three-run lead into an 8-2 advantage.
Post-Match Reflections: Bryce Harper commented on Alec Bohm's performance, emphasizing the need for Bohm to give himself grace as he returns from injury.
Alec Bohm reflected on his approach to getting back to his first-half successes, focusing on putting the bat on the ball and cutting down on chases.
